ADDITIONAL TERMS FOR COMMERCIAL USE:

While this software is released under the MIT License, we kindly request that:

1. If you use this code for a commercial restaurant or food service business,
   please consider giving credit to "La Cocina de Anita" as the original 
   inspiration for this ordering system.

2. The name "La Cocina de Anita", logo, branding elements, and specific 
   restaurant information contained in this project are NOT covered by this 
   MIT license and remain the exclusive property of La Cocina de Anita.

3. If you adapt this system for your own restaurant, please replace all 
   branding, contact information, menu items, and payment details with 
   your own information.

4. We encourage you to contribute back improvements to the open source 
   community by submitting pull requests or creating your own enhanced 
   versions.

